SELECT ms.name AS medical_supply_name, e.equipment_name, i.quantity AS inventory_quantity FROM medical_supplies ms JOIN equipment e ON ms.id = e.id JOIN inventory i ON ms.id = i.item_id WHERE i.quantity > 0;

SELECT s.supplier_name, e.equipment_name, i.quantity FROM suppliers s JOIN equipment e ON s.id = e.id JOIN inventory i ON e.id = i.item_id WHERE i.quantity > 20 AND s.contact_person IS NOT NULL ORDER BY i.quantity DESC;

SELECT ms.name AS medical_supply_name, COUNT(i.id) AS total_items FROM medical_supplies ms JOIN inventory i ON ms.id = i.item_id GROUP BY ms.name HAVING total_items > 5;
SELECT supplier_name, SUM(i.quantity) AS total_quantity FROM suppliers JOIN equipment ON suppliers.id = equipment.id JOIN inventory i ON equipment.id = i.item_id GROUP BY supplier_name;
SELECT supplier_name, COUNT(DISTINCT i.item_id) AS unique_items FROM suppliers JOIN equipment ON suppliers.id = equipment.id JOIN inventory i ON equipment.id = i.item_id GROUP BY supplier_name;

SELECT s.supplier_name, e.equipment_name, COUNT(i.id) AS total_transactions FROM suppliers s JOIN equipment e ON s.id = e.id JOIN inventory i ON e.id = i.item_id GROUP BY s.supplier_name, e.equipment_name HAVING total_transactions > 2;
SELECT ms.name AS medical_supply_name, e.equipment_name, i.quantity AS inventory_quantity FROM medical_supplies ms LEFT JOIN equipment e ON ms.id = e.id LEFT JOIN inventory i ON ms.id = i.item_id;

SELECT s.supplier_name, COALESCE(s.contact_person, 'No Contact Person') AS contact_person, COUNT(i.id) AS total_transactions FROM suppliers s JOIN equipment e ON s.id = e.id JOIN inventory i ON e.id = i.item_id GROUP BY s.supplier_name, s.contact_person;

SELECT ms.name AS medical_supply_name, e.equipment_name, i.quantity AS inventory_quantity FROM medical_supplies ms JOIN equipment e ON ms.id = e.id JOIN inventory i ON ms.id = i.item_id WHERE i.location = 'Storage Room' UNION SELECT ms.name, e.equipment_name, i.quantity FROM medical_supplies ms JOIN equipment e ON ms.id = e.id JOIN inventory i ON ms.id = i.item_id WHERE i.location = 'Supply Room';

SELECT supplier_name, SUM(i.quantity) AS total_quantity FROM suppliers JOIN equipment ON suppliers.id = equipment.id JOIN inventory i ON equipment.id = i.item_id WHERE i.expiration_date > CURRENT_DATE GROUP BY supplier_name;

SELECT ms.name AS medical_supply_name, e.equipment_name, i.quantity AS inventory_quantity FROM medical_supplies ms JOIN equipment e ON ms.id = e.id JOIN inventory i ON ms.id = i.item_id WHERE i.quantity > (SELECT AVG(quantity) FROM inventory);
